These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel, action, crime
House: modern, cottage, cape-cod, townhouse
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
3. the cape-cod house is between the cottage house and the person watching time-travel movies##2
4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching action movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching satire movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime         | time-travel   | action | satire       |
| House      | townhouse | modern | cape-cod   | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, marigold, bellflower, iris
4 different pets are kept: mouse, bird, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the rat is between the person who growsbellflower and the owner of the bird##2
2. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Flower         | marigold | rose | bellflower | iris |
| Pet   | bird    | rat   | mouse | hamster       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, wooden, palace
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, turquise, green, black
1. the person who likes green is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the person who likes green is between the person who likes turquise and the cape-cod house##2
3. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes black is on the left of the wooden house##1
5. the cape-cod house is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| House          | palace    | farmhouse | cape-cod   | wooden  |
| Color   | turquise | green   | black | yellow |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, emerald, purple, light-blue
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, baking, cooking, chess
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person who likes lilac is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who likes light-blue##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Color     | light-blue   | lilac    | purple       | emerald   |
| Hobby   | cooking | chess | reading | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, orchid, tulip, daffodil
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, car, trike
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the skateboard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Flower   | begonia        | tulip | daffodil  | orchid |
| Transport      | car | skateboard  | trike | tram    |

