.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
City: prague, marseilles, paris, miami
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, sprite, almond-milk
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person traveling to miami is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person traveling to paris is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to marseilles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| City   | marseilles     | paris           | prague | miami  |
| Beverage         | 7up | almond-milk | soy-milk   | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, canasta, billiard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, fantasy, horror
1. the person playing whist is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person watching comedy movies and the person playing canasta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game   | billiard   | whist | mah-jongg | canasta      |
| Movie-Genre     | fantasy | comedy    | documentary  | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, coach, firefighter, electrician
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, spanish, nigerian, american
1. the dutch is the coach##1
2. the spanish is between the firefighter and the nigerian##2
3. the project-manager is on the far left##1
4. the dutch is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Job       | project-manager | electrician | firefighter     | coach   |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | spanish     | american | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, disco, techno, salsa
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, aristoff, montecristo, baccarat
1. the fan techno is between the siglo-smoker and the fan ambient##2
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the fan ambient##1
3. the fan salsa is on the right of the fan ambient##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the fan ambient is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Music-Genre         | disco | techno | ambient | salsa |
| Cigar   | siglo         | baccarat       | aristoff    | montecristo         |

