.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, german, french, dutch
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, bird, rat, fish
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the french##1
3. the american is on the right of the german##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the bird is between the german and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality    | dutch   | french      | german   | american  |
| Pet   | fish | bird | rat | rabbit |

