.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, lawyer, police-officer, videographer
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, car, quad-bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the quad-bike is the lawyer##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the tram is the bartender##1
4. the police-officer is the person driving the car##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the videographer##1
6. the person driving the car is between the lawyer and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Job         | lawyer | police-officer | videographer | bartender |
| Transport   | quad-bike          | car     | helicopter  | tram     |

