.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, skydiving, writing, magic-tricks
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, nigerian, canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the turkish and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
3. the nigerian is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby           | cooking | magic-tricks | skydiving | writing     |
| Nationality   | argentine   | canadian    | turkish   | nigerian |

