.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, cooking, reading, skydiving
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, fonseca, pall-mall, montecristo
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is between the montecristo-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##2
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Hobby           | hiking | skydiving | reading | cooking |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | cain | montecristo         | pall-mall |

