.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, mexican, colombian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, mirinda, cola
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the australian##1
2. the colombian is between the person drinking cola and the american##2
