4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Nationality         | american      | colombian | australian  | mexican |
| Beverage   | fanta | mirinda  | cola | iced-tea    |

