.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, january, june, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, biathlon, rugby, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's birthday is in january##2
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | august | january | june | july |
| Sport     | rowing     | biathlon   | parkour | rugby  |

