.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, 7up
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, march, june, october
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | coffee |
| Birthday           | june  | october  | march | august      |

