3. the person who likes coral is between the software-developer and the person who likes brown##2
4. the person who likes azure is the software-developer##1
5. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Color       | azure | coral | brown | emerald |
| Job   | software-developer    | analyst  | paramedic    | project-manager       |

