.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, puzzles, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, scientist, nurse, coach
1. the scientist is on the left of the coach##1
2. the writer is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the writer##1
4. the coach is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | fishing   | camping   | filmmaking | puzzles |
| Job         | writer | scientist | coach     | nurse    |

