.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
City: marseilles, san-francisco, new-york, boston
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, gospel, r&b, rock
1. the fan gospel is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is between the fan reggae and the person traveling to boston##2
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the fan r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| City   | new-york    | boston     | marseilles | san-francisco |
| Music-Genre     | gospel | rock | r&b       | reggae     |

 